      "lean_file_body": "open Finset BigOperators\n\nnamespace AlgebraicCombinatorics.SubtractiveMethods\n\ntheorem cancel_all_even_l1 (n d : ℕ) :\n    (∑ e : Fin d → ZMod 2, (∑ k : Fin d, toSign (e k)) ^ n) =\n      ∑ x : Fin n → Fin d, ∑ e : Fin d → ZMod 2, signProduct e x := by\n  calc\n    (∑ e : Fin d → ZMod 2, (∑ k : Fin d, toSign (e k)) ^ n)\n        = ∑ e : Fin d → ZMod 2, ∑ x : Fin n → Fin d, signProduct e x := by\n      apply Finset.sum_congr rfl\n      intro e _\n      simp [signProduct, Finset.sum_pow]\n    _ = ∑ x : Fin n → Fin d, ∑ e : Fin d → ZMod 2, signProduct e x := by\n      rw [Finset.sum_comm]\n\nend AlgebraicCombinatorics.SubtractiveMethods",
      "notes": [
        "Expands each power of a finite sum over signs into the sum over functions Fin n → Fin d, using the project definition signProduct, then interchanges the two finite sums."
